  paid as a lump sum with the second monthly salary; if entitlement
  ends early the staff member must refund the part of the provisional
  payment proportionate to the unexpired portion of the three‑month
  period. The supplement (see below) is paid after completion of the
  period. - Supplement: A maximum supplement of EUR 2,070 may be paid
