  likely conflict of interest; authorisation will be granted only if
  those conditions are met and may be subject to conditions (including
  restrictions on hours).  Key details and steps 1. Need for
  authorisation    - Written authorisation is required for
  occupational external activities (ECB Staff Rules §0.2.6.1).  2.
  Exception (paid vs unpaid)    - No authorisation is required for
  external activities that are both (i) unremunerated and (ii) in
  certain benevolent domains (e.g. culture, science, education, sport,
