  shall decide on the request within five working days; it may attach
  conditions (§0.4.2.6).  5. Conditions, duration and termination    -
  Authorisation will be granted only if the activity “does not in any
  way impair the performance of the member of staff’s professional
  duties towards the ECB and does not constitute a likely source of
